Aria Cognitive Memory (`aria_acm`) is an independent copy of ACM (Aria Cognitive
Memory engine), derived from the certified standalone ACM repository
(Apache-2.0). Modifications inside Aria do not update the standalone project
unless explicitly contributed upstream. Automatic synchronization is forbidden.
Standalone ACM remains the research and reference implementation.

